  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Sauté diced onion and minced garlic for 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add cubed sweet potato and cook for 5 minutes until slightly tender.",
    "Stir in cured chorizo, cook for 1 minute until warmed through.",
    "Add king prawns, cook for 2 minutes until pink and opaque.",
    "Pour in coconut milk and chicken stock, then add cinnamon and red pepper flakes.",
    "Simmer for 5 minutes until the sauce thickens slightly and prawns are cooked through.",
    "Serve hot with a sprinkle of fresh cilantro for garnish."
